  <title>Distinguish Between Section and SectX Elements</title>
  <info>
    <definitions definitionfile="defs.xml"/>
  </info>
  
  <section role="problem">
    <title>Problem</title>
    <para>You need to know what are the differences and advantages of
      using a <tag>section</tag> over a <tag>sectX</tag> element.</para>
  </section>
  <section role="solution">
    <title>Solution</title>
    <para>The difference between <tag>section</tag> against
      <tag>sectX</tag> are depicted in <xref linkend="tab.section.vs.sectx.comparison"/>: </para>
    
    <table xml:id="tab.section.vs.sectx.comparison">
      <title>Comparison Between <tag>section</tag> and <tag>sectX</tag></title>
      <tgroup cols="3">
        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry>Issue</entry>
            <entry><tag>section</tag></entry>
            <entry><tag>sectX</tag></entry>
          </row>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry>Nesting Level</entry>
            <entry>Undefinied<footnote>
              <para>Can be restricted through DocBook customization, see
              <link xlink:href="http://www.docbook.org/tdg51/en/html/ch05.html#ex.limitsdepth"/>.</para>
            </footnote></entry>
            <entry>Up to <tag>sect5</tag></entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Readability</entry>
            <entry>Worse</entry>
            <entry>Better</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Easy Relocation</entry>
            <entry>Yes</entry>
            <entry>No, needs to be renamed</entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>Renaming after relocation</entry>
            <entry>Not needed</entry>
            <entry>Needs to be renamed</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </table>
  </section>
  <section role="discussion">
    <title>Discussion</title>
    <para>Some discussion about problem and solution.</para>
  </section>
